metadata.description:
The convergence of man and machine draws us closer to a future of cyberpunk dystopia. As technology advances, we are becoming more dependent on it and the lines between human and artificial intelligence blur. The once-clear distinction between reality and virtuality is fading, and we are left to wonder what will become of us in a world where the boundaries of what is real and what is not are no longer clear. Will we find ourselves lost in a digital labyrinth, a mere shadow of our former selves, or will we emerge stronger, transcending our human limitations? Only time will tell.

I'm trapped in a digital maze, hunted by shadows that flicker and glitch.
